name: Great Ape
description: GREATAPE is a community token built on Binance Smart Chain by the one and only creator of the Reflect function. GREATAPE is a fully decentralized protocol improved upon Safemoon's code by fixing the security flaws and reducing gas costs by up to 70%. Stealth launched with a limit of 100m tokens per TX to prevent whale manipulation. Ownership was renounced before launch and the contract launch method was called by the community after 40 BNB was sent to the contract address for liquidity.
